{
  "stem": "3973.3",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But this was-- once people began to die, it was sort of make more room because the bodies could be stacked in one corner.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] We arrived to Mauthausen.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That's a story in itself.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We were thirsty.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The thirst was unbelievable.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was just trying to remember what it feels like.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Because after several days on the train, and then still no water.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Finally we got to the showers.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We didn't know whether they were gas chambers or not, but when water came in, my, that was something.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They assigned us to the blocks.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So many of us, that they put us in-- people just sitting, like-- like this.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And then they would shove other people and form these long rows.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And this is how we spent the night.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And then they would take us to the famous stone quarry.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "The quarry at Mauthausen was a granite quarry.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "It was in a bottom of the big pit.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And there were 186 steps cut in the rock.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "We were there in 1965 for a trip.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So the Austrian government had made the steps, cut them down to different sizes in order for the tourists to be able to go.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But there were some steps which were as high as to meters high.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so-- I mean, they cut in the rock.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there was no-- well, [INAUDIBLE] tell you was what they were doing is they marched us through these stone quarries barefoot, on hard granite, I mean, sharp granite.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We would go down, and two people would load up a stone on your back.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And you had to climb up.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There's no way of climbing up on a two meter stone.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
